name: Deleted entry
classes: Acting on other nitrogenous compounds as donors;
comment: Deleted entry: 5,10-methylenetetrahydrofolate reductase (FADH2). Now included with EC 1.5.1.20, methylenetetrahydrofolate reductase [NAD(P)H]. Based on the reference, it had been thought that this was a separate enzyme from EC 1.5.1.20 but the reference upon which the entry was based has since been disproved
